      <title>尼日尔因涉嫌支持马里叛军而与乌克兰断绝关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/niger-cuts-ties-with-ukraine-over-its-alleged-backing-of-malian-rebels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日尔军政府与马里一道，因乌克兰涉嫌支持马里叛军而断绝了与乌克兰的外交关系。]]></description>
