    <item>
      <title>哈马斯新政治领袖辛瓦尔有着狡猾而残暴的过去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/hamas-new-political-chief-sinwar-has-a-cunning-and-brutal-past</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大约六年前，刚刚被任命为​​哈马斯政治领袖的叶海亚·辛瓦尔在一份文件上潦草地写了一张便条，他知道埃及中间人会将这份文件交给以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/hamas-new-political-chief-sinwar-has-a-cunning-and-brutal-past</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:15:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
