      <title>中国释放被拘留四个月的台湾渔民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/china-frees-taiwanese-fisherman-it-detained-for-four-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国释放了一名被关押四个多月的台湾渔民，而此次拘留发生在北京海警似乎在台北近海前哨基地周围采取军事行动之际。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/china-frees-taiwanese-fisherman-it-detained-for-four-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:06:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
